OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FArrests for offences linked to people
OL,7,Fsmuggling involving the National Crime
OL,8,FAgency have gone up by more than 55%
OL,9,Fin a year, the organisation has said.
OL,11,FThe NCA was involved in 300 arrests
OL,12,Fboth in the UK and overseas in the
OL,13,Fyear to April 2026, up from 190 the
OL,14,Fyear before, new figures reveal.
OL,16,FThe rise is said to follow an increase
OL,17,Fin resources with more officers
OL,18,Fworking to focus only on organised
OL,19,Fimmigration crime, the agency added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
