OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779069821
OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,F"The NCA's role is to target the
OL,7,Forganised gangs behind people
OL,8,Fsmuggling, and we use our full range
OL,9,Fof law enforcement tactics to disrupt
OL,10,Fand dismantle networks wherever they
OL,11,Foperate, preventing harm to those they
OL,12,Fexploit for profit, protecting lives
OL,13,Fand the UK's border security," NCA
OL,14,Fdirector of general operations Rob
OL,15,FJones said.
OL,17,F"Tackling organised immigration crime
OL,18,Fremains a top priority for the NCA,
OL,19,Fand we are putting more resource into
OL,20,Ftargeting the criminal networks behind
OL,21,Fit than ever before.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
