PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779069821
OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,F"We are also taking the fight against
OL,7,Fthe gangs outside of Europe to
OL,8,Flocations like Iraq and Libya,
OL,9,Ftargeting criminal networks who are
OL,10,Foperating in locations where they
OL,11,Fpreviously thought themselves
OL,12,Funtouchable."
OL,14,FOver the 2025 to 2026 period, some 59
OL,15,Fpeople were convicted of organised
OL,16,Fimmigration crime (OIC) offences in UK
OL,17,Fcourts following NCA investigations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@MO]
