OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis includes UK-based people smuggler
OL,12,FAhmed Ebid, who was jailed for 25
OL,13,Fyears in May last year after he
OL,14,Fexploited migrants as part of a #12
OL,15,Fmillion illegal boat crossing
OL,16,Foperation.
OL,18,FEgyptian-born Ebid helped organise the
OL,19,Fmovement of thousands migrants on boat
OL,20,Fcrossings from North Africa into
OL,21,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
