OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FTurkish national Adem Savas was also
OL,7,Fsentenced to 11 years in prison in
OL,8,FJanuary 2026 after an investigation
OL,9,Finvolving the NCA and Belgian
OL,10,Fauthorities.
OL,12,FJones said Savas was the "most
OL,13,Fsignificant supplier of boats and
OL,14,Fengines to people smuggling gangs
OL,15,Finvolved in organising deadly
OL,16,Fcrossings in the Channel" after his
OL,17,Fsentencing earlier this year.
OL,26,@tD@ZOUxD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
