PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779069821
OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FIt was reported that the NCA believed
OL,7,Fthat in 2023, Savas supplied equipment
OL,8,Fused in around half of all Channel
OL,9,Fcrossings, making him the agency's
OL,10,Fmost wanted man as a key player in
OL,11,FEuropean people smuggling circles.
OL,13,FIn January and February this year, the
OL,14,FNCA arrested six people for people
OL,15,Fsmuggling offences after a lorry
OL,16,Fcontaining 23 people was stopped at
OL,17,FDover port in Kent.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
