OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FIn March, NCA officers took part in an
OL,7,Foperation in Germany that saw four
OL,8,Fpeople arrested as part of an
OL,9,Foperation targeting another network
OL,10,Fsupplying equipment to small boat
OL,11,Fgangs.
OL,13,FJones added: "As these cases show, we
OL,14,Faim to target people smuggling
OL,15,Forganised crime groups at every step
OL,16,Fof the route, in source countries, in
OL,17,Ftransit countries, near the UK border
OL,18,Fin France and Belgium, and those
OL,19,Foperating inside the UK itself.
OL,26,@uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
