PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779069821
OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,F"We know our activity is having an
OL,7,Fimpact, we are having a disruptive
OL,8,Feffect on OCGs, and we are making the
OL,9,FUK a more difficult place for them to
OL,10,Ftarget."
OL,12,FDuring the 2025 to 2026 financial
OL,13,Fyear, the NCA led on 400 disruptions
OL,14,Fagainst OIC networks ` up from 350 in
OL,15,Fthe previous year.
OL,17,FMinister for Border Security and
OL,18,FAsylum, Alex Norris, said: "This
OL,19,FGovernment is delivering the biggest
OL,20,Fcrackdown on people smuggling ever
OL,21,Fseen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]zD@\OU
