PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779069821
OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,F"Dedicated efforts from our National
OL,7,FCrime Agency officers have driven a
OL,8,F55% surge in organised immigration
OL,9,Fcrime arrests ` ramping up action to
OL,10,Ftackle the gangs behind this trade.
OL,12,F"This comes as we've launched a record-
OL,13,Fbreaking number of enforcement
OL,14,Factions, including arrests and
OL,15,Fsanctions, against migrant smuggling
OL,16,Fnetworks since coming into office.
OL,18,F"Make no mistake, we will track down,
OL,19,Fdetain and arrest the vile criminals
OL,20,Fwho bring illegal migrants to our
OL,21,Fshores."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@HO]
