OL,3,CArrests over people smuggling rose by
OL,4,C55% in last year, says NCA
OL,6,FIn 2025 the NCA's work with
OL,7,Finternational authorities saw more
OL,8,Fthan 500 boats and engines seized.
OL,10,FThat same year it worked with social
OL,11,Fmedia networks to have more than
OL,12,F10,000 accounts, posts or pages linked
OL,13,Fto organised immigration crime removed
OL,14,Ffrom their platforms.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
